---
title: Miso-Honey Glazed Salmon with Sesame Rice and Sautéed Veggies
description: A sweet and savoury pair seldom disappoints! We're coating salmon with a winning miso and honey combo, before roasting it to create a beautifully-caramelized finish. Sautéed veggies provide gorgeous colour, while sesame rice rounds out the plate!
